Hardware Requirements:
1. Raspberry Pi Model A/B/B+ 
2. ADS1115 ADC.
3. Breadboard.
4. Jumper Wires


Connections:
VDD Pin 17
GND Pin 9
SCL Pin 5
SDA Pin 3 

Terminal:
sudo raspi-config  #Interfacing Options → I2C → Enable (Yes)
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade
sudo apt-get install build-essential python3-dev python3-smbus git.
git clone https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit/Adafruit_Python_ADS1x15.git
